  The Johnson’s Star, Susan Pwojak has confirmed her relationship with Nigerian singer Michael Adebayo, popularly known as Ruger. Susan shared a slideshow of their loved up moments with a song by Charlie Puth and Wiz Khalifa’s “See You Again” playing at the background on Instagram. It had the lyrics “First, you both go out your way and the vibe is feeling strong. And what’s small turned to a friendship, a friendship turned to a bond. And that bond will never be broken, the love will never get lost (the love will never get lost)”  Recall the 37-year-old got married to a fitness trainer Maje Ayida on the 15th of January 2014, after dating for 8 years but the marriage lasted for 18 months before it crashed, after Maje impregnated his ex-girlfriend.